text: Alderney (Aurigny) is an island in the Channel Islands. Alderney may also refer to: * Alderney, Dorset * States of Alderney, parliament and council of the island * Air Alderney, airline serving the island * Alderney cattle, an extinct breed of dairy cattle * HMS Alderney, multiple ships * Alderney, fictional place in video game Grand Theft Auto IV (2008) ==See also== * *
title: Alderney (disambiguation)
